        public InspectionToolWrapper getInspectionTool(java.lang.String shortName,
                                               Project project)
        Warning: Usage of this method is discouraged as if separate tool options are defined for different scopes, it just returns the options for the first scope which may lead to unexpected results. Consider using getInspectionTool(String, PsiElement) instead.
        Parameters:
        shortName - an inspection short name
        project - a project
        Returns:
        an InspectionToolWrapper associated with this tool.
